question: projects of the institution "Royal Veterinary College" that started after 2014
sql_query: SELECT * FROM institutions AS T1 JOIN project_members AS T13 ON T1.unics_id = T13.institution_id JOIN projects AS T2 ON T13.project = T2.unics_id WHERE T1.institutions_name like '%Royal Veterinary College%' and T2.start_year > 2014
sparql_query: SELECT    ?title ?projAcronym ?ecObjective ?cordisRef ?ecRef ?frameworkProgram   ?startYear ?endYear ?totalCost ?ecMaxContribution   ?orgName ?partRCN ?picNumber ?ecContribution   ?role ?activityTypeCode ?activityType   ?city ?country ?nuts3Code ?nuts2Code ?nuts1Code WHERE {   ?proj a dbo:EC-Project .   ?proj dbo:ecParticipant ?part .   ?part dbo:organization ?org .   ?org dbo:extendedName ?orgName .   FILTER (regex(?orgName, "Royal Veterinary College", "i"))      ?proj dbo:title ?title .   ?proj dbo:acronym ?projAcronym .   ?proj dbo:ecObjective ?ecObjective .   ?proj dbo:cordisRef ?cordisRef .   ?proj dbo:ecRef ?ecRef .   ?proj dbo:ecFrameworkProgram ?fp .   ?fp dbo:extendedName ?frameworkProgram .   optional { ?proj dbo:startingYear ?startYear . }   optional { ?proj dbo:endYear ?endYear . }   ?proj dbo:totalCost ?totalCost .   ?proj dbo:ecMaxContribution ?ecMaxContribution .      ?part dbo:rcn ?partRCN .   optional { ?part dbo:picNumber ?picNumber . }   optional { ?part dbo:ecContribution ?ecContribution . }   ?part dbo:roleInProject ?roleInProject .   ?roleInProject dbo:extendedName ?role .   ?part dbo:ecActivityType ?at .   ?at dbo:identifier ?activityTypeCode .   ?at dbo:extendedName ?activityType .   ?part dbo:cityName ?city .   ?part dbo:country ?cou .   ?cou dbo:extendedName ?country .   optional { ?part dbo:nuts3 ?nuts3 . ?nuts3 dbo:identifier ?nuts3Code . }   optional { ?part dbo:nuts2 ?nuts2 . ?nuts2 dbo:identifier ?nuts2Code . }   optional { ?part dbo:nuts1 ?nuts1 . ?nuts1 dbo:identifier ?nuts1Code . } }

question: projects whose beneficiaries are in the city of BUDAPEST and have activity type PRC
sql_query: SELECT * FROM projects AS T1 JOIN project_members AS T2 ON T1.unics_id = T2.project WHERE T2.city like 'BUDAPEST' and T2.activity_type = 'PRC'
sparql_query: SELECT    ?title ?projAcronym ?ecObjective ?cordisRef ?ecRef ?frameworkProgram   ?startYear ?endYear ?totalCost ?ecMaxContribution   ?orgName ?partRCN ?picNumber ?ecContribution   ?role ?activityTypeCode ?activityType   ?city ?country ?nuts3Code ?nuts2Code ?nuts1Code WHERE {   ?proj a dbo:EC-Project .   ?proj dbo:ecParticipant ?part .   ?part dbo:organization ?org .   ?org dbo:extendedName ?orgName .      ?proj dbo:title ?title .   ?proj dbo:acronym ?projAcronym .   ?proj dbo:ecObjective ?ecObjective .   ?proj dbo:cordisRef ?cordisRef .   ?proj dbo:ecRef ?ecRef .   ?proj dbo:ecFrameworkProgram ?fp .   ?fp dbo:extendedName ?frameworkProgram .   optional { ?proj dbo:startingYear ?startYear . }   optional { ?proj dbo:endYear ?endYear . }   ?proj dbo:totalCost ?totalCost .   ?proj dbo:ecMaxContribution ?ecMaxContribution .      ?part dbo:rcn ?partRCN .   optional { ?part dbo:picNumber ?picNumber . }   optional { ?part dbo:ecContribution ?ecContribution . }   ?part dbo:roleInProject ?roleInProject .   ?roleInProject dbo:extendedName ?role .   ?part dbo:ecActivityType ?at .   ?at dbo:identifier ?activityTypeCode .   ?at dbo:extendedName ?activityType .   FILTER (?activityTypeCode = 'PRC')   ?part dbo:cityName ?city .   FILTER (regex(?city, "^BUDAPEST$", "i"))   ?part dbo:country ?cou .   ?cou dbo:extendedName ?country .   optional { ?part dbo:nuts3 ?nuts3 . ?nuts3 dbo:identifier ?nuts3Code . }   optional { ?part dbo:nuts2 ?nuts2 . ?nuts2 dbo:identifier ?nuts2Code . }   optional { ?part dbo:nuts1 ?nuts1 . ?nuts1 dbo:identifier ?nuts1Code . } }

question: projects of the institution "Cardiff University" with programme short name "MSCA Mobility" ordered by year

question: projects with programme short name Biotechnology and funding scheme code "SME-1"
sql_query: SELECT * FROM projects AS T2 JOIN project_programmes AS T1 ON T1.project = T2.unics_id JOIN programmes AS T4 ON T1.programme = T4.code WHERE T4.short_name like '%Biotechnology%' and T2.ec_fund_scheme = 'SME-1'
sparql_query: SELECT    ?title ?projAcronym ?ecObjective ?cordisRef ?ecRef ?frameworkProgram   ?startYear ?endYear ?totalCost ?ecMaxContribution   ?progId ?progName ?progShortName ?fundingScheme WHERE {   ?proj a dbo:EC-Project .      ?proj dbo:title ?title .   ?proj dbo:acronym ?projAcronym .   ?proj dbo:ecObjective ?ecObjective .   ?proj dbo:cordisRef ?cordisRef .   ?proj dbo:ecRef ?ecRef .   ?proj dbo:ecFrameworkProgram ?fp .   ?fp dbo:extendedName ?frameworkProgram .   optional { ?proj dbo:startingYear ?startYear . }   optional { ?proj dbo:endYear ?endYear . }   ?proj dbo:totalCost ?totalCost .   ?proj dbo:ecMaxContribution ?ecMaxContribution .    ?proj dbo:ecProgramme ?prog .   ?prog dbo:identifier ?progId .   ?prog dbo:extendedName ?progName .   ?prog dbo:shortName ?progShortName .   FILTER (regex(?progShortName, "Biotechnology", "i"))    ?proj dbo:ecFundingScheme ?fs .   ?fs dbo:shortName ?fundingScheme .   FILTER (?fundingScheme = "SME-1") }

question: institutions and funding received in descending order
sql_query: SELECT T1.institutions_name, sum(T3.ec_contribution) FROM institutions AS T1 JOIN project_members AS T3 ON T1.unics_id = T3.institution_id GROUP BY T1.institutions_name ORDER BY sum(T3.ec_contribution) DESC

question: count projects per country with programme short name "Science with and for Society"
sql_query: SELECT T5.country_name, count(distinct T1.unics_id) FROM projects AS T1 JOIN project_members AS T2 ON T1.unics_id = T2.project JOIN project_programmes AS T14 ON T1.unics_id = T14.project JOIN programmes AS T3 ON T14.programme = T3.code JOIN institutions AS T4 ON T4.unics_id = T2.institution_id JOIN countries AS T5 ON T5.unics_id = T4.country_id WHERE T3.short_name like '%Science with and for Society%' GROUP BY T5.country_name

question: erc panels and sum of project ec max contribution ordered descending
sql_query: SELECT T1.code, SUM(T2.ec_max_contribution) FROM erc_panels AS T1 JOIN project_erc_panels AS T3 ON T1.code = T3.panel JOIN projects AS T2 on T3.project = T2.unics_id GROUP BY T1.code ORDER BY SUM(T2.ec_max_contribution)
sparql_query: SELECT    ?ercPanelId ?ercPanelName (sum(?ecMaxContribution) AS ?sumOfEcMaxContribution) WHERE {   ?proj a dbo:EC-Project .      ?proj dbo:title ?title .   ?proj dbo:acronym ?projAcronym .   ?proj dbo:ecObjective ?ecObjective .   ?proj dbo:cordisRef ?cordisRef .   ?proj dbo:ecRef ?ecRef .   ?proj dbo:ecFrameworkProgram ?fp .   ?fp dbo:extendedName ?frameworkProgram .   optional { ?proj dbo:startingYear ?startYear . }   optional { ?proj dbo:endYear ?endYear . }   ?proj dbo:totalCost ?totalCost .   ?proj dbo:ecMaxContribution ?ecMaxContribution .    ?proj dbo:ercPanel ?ercPanel .   ?ercPanel dbo:identifier ?ercPanelId .   ?ercPanel dbo:extendedName ?ercPanelName . } GROUP BY ?ercPanelId ?ercPanelName ORDER BY DESC(?sumOfEcMaxContribution)

sparql_query: SELECT    ?title ?projAcronym ?ecObjective ?cordisRef ?ecRef ?frameworkProgram   ?startYear ?endYear ?totalCost ?ecMaxContribution   ?orgName ?partRCN ?picNumber ?ecContribution   ?role ?activityTypeCode ?activityType   ?city ?country ?nuts3Code ?nuts2Code ?nuts1Code WHERE {   ?proj a dbo:EC-Project .   ?proj dbo:ecParticipant ?part .   ?part dbo:organization ?org .   ?org dbo:extendedName ?orgName .      ?proj dbo:title ?title .   ?proj dbo:acronym ?projAcronym .   ?proj dbo:ecObjective ?ecObjective .   ?proj dbo:cordisRef ?cordisRef .   ?proj dbo:ecRef ?ecRef .   ?proj dbo:ecFrameworkProgram ?fp .   ?fp dbo:extendedName ?frameworkProgram .   FILTER (?frameworkProgram = "H2020")   optional { ?proj dbo:startingYear ?startYear . }   optional { ?proj dbo:endYear ?endYear . }   ?proj dbo:totalCost ?totalCost .   ?proj dbo:ecMaxContribution ?ecMaxContribution .      ?part dbo:rcn ?partRCN .   optional { ?part dbo:picNumber ?picNumber . }   optional { ?part dbo:ecContribution ?ecContribution . }   ?part dbo:roleInProject ?roleInProject .   ?roleInProject dbo:extendedName ?role .   ?part dbo:ecActivityType ?at .   ?at dbo:identifier ?activityTypeCode .   ?at dbo:extendedName ?activityType .   ?part dbo:cityName ?city .   ?part dbo:country ?cou .   ?cou dbo:extendedName ?country .   FILTER (regex(?country, "^Italy$", "i"))   optional { ?part dbo:nuts3 ?nuts3 . ?nuts3 dbo:identifier ?nuts3Code . }   optional { ?part dbo:nuts2 ?nuts2 . ?nuts2 dbo:identifier ?nuts2Code . }   optional { ?part dbo:nuts1 ?nuts1 . ?nuts1 dbo:identifier ?nuts1Code . } }

FILTER (regex(?projAcronym, "^ALFRED$", "i"))   ?proj dbo:ecObjective ?ecObjective .   ?proj dbo:cordisRef ?cordisRef .   ?proj dbo:ecRef ?ecRef .   ?proj dbo:ecFrameworkProgram ?fp .   ?fp dbo:extendedName ?frameworkProgram .   optional { ?proj dbo:startingYear ?startYear . }   optional { ?proj dbo:endYear ?endYear . }   ?proj dbo:totalCost ?totalCost .   ?proj dbo:ecMaxContribution ?ecMaxContribution .      ?part dbo:rcn ?partRCN .   optional { ?part dbo:picNumber ?picNumber . }   optional { ?part dbo:ecContribution ?ecContribution . }   ?part dbo:roleInProject ?roleInProject .   ?roleInProject dbo:extendedName ?role .   ?part dbo:ecActivityType ?at .   ?at dbo:identifier ?activityTypeCode .   ?at dbo:extendedName ?activityType .   ?part dbo:cityName ?city .   ?part dbo:country ?cou .   ?cou dbo:extendedName ?country .   optional { ?part dbo:nuts3 ?nuts3 . ?nuts3 dbo:identifier ?nuts3Code . }   optional { ?part dbo:nuts2 ?nuts2 . ?nuts2 dbo:identifier ?nuts2Code . }   optional { ?part dbo:nuts1 ?nuts1 . ?nuts1 dbo:identifier ?nuts1Code . } }

question: List all projects under the "FP7-ICT" programme
sql_query: SELECT * FROM projects AS T2 JOIN project_programmes AS T1 ON T1.project = T2.unics_id JOIN programmes AS T3 on T1.programme = T3.code WHERE T3.code like 'FP7-ICT%'
sparql_query: SELECT    ?title ?projAcronym ?ecObjective ?cordisRef ?ecRef ?frameworkProgram   ?startYear ?endYear ?totalCost ?ecMaxContribution   ?progId ?progName ?progShortName WHERE {   ?proj a dbo:EC-Project .      ?proj dbo:title ?title .   ?proj dbo:acronym ?projAcronym .   ?proj dbo:ecObjective ?ecObjective .   ?proj dbo:cordisRef ?cordisRef .   ?proj dbo:ecRef ?ecRef .   ?proj dbo:ecFrameworkProgram ?fp .   ?fp dbo:extendedName ?frameworkProgram .   optional { ?proj dbo:startingYear ?startYear . }   optional { ?proj dbo:endYear ?endYear . }   ?proj dbo:totalCost ?totalCost .   ?proj dbo:ecMaxContribution ?ecMaxContribution .    ?proj dbo:ecProgramme ?prog .   ?prog dbo:identifier ?progId .   ?prog dbo:extendedName ?progName .   ?prog dbo:shortName ?progShortName .   FILTER (regex(?progId, "^FP7-ICT", "i")) }

question: Find the role of ATHENA in project ARGOS
sql_query: SELECT T1.member_role FROM project_members AS T1 JOIN projects AS T2 ON T1.project = T2.unics_id JOIN institutions AS T3 ON T3.unics_id = T1.institution_id  WHERE T2.acronym like 'ARGOS' and T3.institutions_name like '%ATHENA%'
sparql_query: SELECT    ?role  WHERE {   ?proj a dbo:EC-Project .   ?proj dbo:ecParticipant ?part .   ?part dbo:organization ?org .   ?org dbo:extendedName ?orgName .   FILTER (regex(?orgName, "ATHENA", "i"))      ?proj dbo:title ?title .   ?proj dbo:acronym ?projAcronym .   FILTER (regex(?projAcronym, "^ARGOS$", "i"))   ?proj dbo:ecObjective ?ecObjective .   ?proj dbo:cordisRef ?cordisRef .   ?proj dbo:ecRef ?ecRef .   ?proj dbo:ecFrameworkProgram ?fp .   ?fp dbo:extendedName ?frameworkProgram .   optional { ?proj dbo:startingYear ?startYear . }   optional { ?proj dbo:endYear ?endYear . }   ?proj dbo:totalCost ?totalCost .   ?proj dbo:ecMaxContribution ?ecMaxContribution .      ?part dbo:rcn ?partRCN .   optional { ?part dbo:picNumber ?picNumber . }   optional { ?part dbo:ecContribution ?ecContribution . }   ?part dbo:roleInProject ?roleInProject .   ?roleInProject dbo:extendedName ?role .   ?part dbo:ecActivityType ?at .   ?at dbo:identifier ?activityTypeCode .   ?at dbo:extendedName ?activityType .   ?part dbo:cityName ?city .   ?part dbo:country ?cou .   ?cou dbo:extendedName ?country .   optional { ?part dbo:nuts3 ?nuts3 . ?nuts3 dbo:identifier ?nuts3Code . }   optional { ?part dbo:nuts2 ?nuts2 . ?nuts2 dbo:identifier ?nuts2Code . }   optional { ?part dbo:nuts1 ?nuts1 . ?nuts1 dbo:identifier ?nuts1Code . } }

question: Return projects of research organisations located in Greece
sql_query: SELECT * FROM project_members AS T1 JOIN projects AS T2 ON T1.project = T2.unics_id JOIN institutions AS T3 ON T3.unics_id = T1.institution_id JOIN countries AS T4 ON T3.country_id = T4.unics_id WHERE T1.activity_type = 'REC' and T4.country_name like 'Greece'
sparql_query: SELECT    ?title ?projAcronym ?ecObjective ?cordisRef ?ecRef ?frameworkProgram   ?startYear ?endYear ?totalCost ?ecMaxContribution   ?orgName ?partRCN ?picNumber ?ecContribution   ?role ?activityTypeCode ?activityType   ?city ?country ?nuts3Code ?nuts2Code ?nuts1Code WHERE {   ?proj a dbo:EC-Project .   ?proj dbo:ecParticipant ?part .   ?part dbo:organization ?org .   ?org dbo:extendedName ?orgName .      ?proj dbo:title ?title .   ?proj dbo:acronym ?projAcronym .   ?proj dbo:ecObjective ?ecObjective .   ?proj dbo:cordisRef ?cordisRef .   ?proj dbo:ecRef ?ecRef .   ?proj dbo:ecFrameworkProgram ?fp .   ?fp dbo:extendedName ?frameworkProgram .   optional { ?proj dbo:startingYear ?startYear . }   optional { ?proj dbo:endYear ?endYear . }   ?proj dbo:totalCost ?totalCost .   ?proj dbo:ecMaxContribution ?ecMaxContribution .      ?part dbo:rcn ?partRCN .   optional { ?part dbo:picNumber ?picNumber . }   optional { ?part dbo:ecContribution ?ecContribution . }   ?part dbo:roleInProject ?roleInProject .   ?roleInProject dbo:extendedName ?role .   ?part dbo:ecActivityType ?at .   ?at dbo:identifier ?activityTypeCode .   FILTER (?activityTypeCode = "REC")   ?at dbo:extendedName ?activityType .   ?part dbo:cityName ?city .   ?part dbo:country ?cou .   ?cou dbo:extendedName ?country .   FILTER (regex(?country, "^Greece$", "i"))   optional { ?part dbo:nuts3 ?nuts3 . ?nuts3 dbo:identifier ?nuts3Code . }   optional { ?part dbo:nuts2 ?nuts2 . ?nuts2 dbo:identifier ?nuts2Code . }   optional { ?part dbo:nuts1 ?nuts1 . ?nuts1 dbo:identifier ?nuts1Code . } }

question: Find all projects with beneficiaries located in the Schaffhausen area
sql_query: SELECT * FROM projects AS T1 JOIN project_members AS T2 on T1.unics_id = T2.project JOIN institutions AS T3 ON T2.institution_id = T3.unics_id JOIN eu_territorial_units AS T4 ON T2.geocode_regions_3 = T4.geocode_regions WHERE T4.description like 'Schaffhausen'
sparql_query: SELECT    ?title ?projAcronym ?ecObjective ?cordisRef ?ecRef ?frameworkProgram   ?startYear ?endYear ?totalCost ?ecMaxContribution   ?orgName ?partRCN ?picNumber ?ecContribution   ?role ?activityTypeCode ?activityType   ?city ?country ?nuts3Code ?nuts2Code ?nuts1Code WHERE {   ?proj a dbo:EC-Project .   ?proj dbo:ecParticipant ?part .   ?part dbo:organization ?org .   ?org dbo:extendedName ?orgName .      ?proj dbo:title ?title .   ?proj dbo:acronym ?projAcronym .   ?proj dbo:ecObjective ?ecObjective .   ?proj dbo:cordisRef ?cordisRef .   ?proj dbo:ecRef ?ecRef .   ?proj dbo:ecFrameworkProgram ?fp .   ?fp dbo:extendedName ?frameworkProgram .   optional { ?proj dbo:startingYear ?startYear . }   optional { ?proj dbo:endYear ?endYear . }   ?proj dbo:totalCost ?totalCost .   ?proj dbo:ecMaxContribution ?ecMaxContribution .      ?part dbo:rcn ?partRCN .   optional { ?part dbo:picNumber ?picNumber . }   optional { ?part dbo:ecContribution ?ecContribution . }   ?part dbo:roleInProject ?roleInProject .   ?roleInProject dbo:extendedName ?role .   ?part dbo:ecActivityType ?at .   ?at dbo:identifier ?activityTypeCode .   ?at dbo:extendedName ?activityType .   ?part dbo:cityName ?city .   ?part dbo:country ?cou .   ?cou dbo:extendedName ?country .   ?part dbo:nuts3 ?nuts3 . ?nuts3 dbo:identifier ?nuts3Code .   ?nuts3 dbo:extendedName ?nuts3Name .   FILTER (regex(?nuts3Name, "^Schaffhausen$", "i"))   optional { ?part dbo:nuts2 ?nuts2 . ?nuts2 dbo:identifier ?nuts2Code . }   optional { ?part dbo:nuts1 ?nuts1 . ?nuts1 dbo:identifier ?nuts1Code . } }
